<section class="oe_container">
   <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
        <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:olive;"><b>Document / Attachment Versioning</b></h2>
<p style="color:olive;">This app allow you to have document version on attachment records.
        <p>
            <b style="color:CRIMSON;">Main Features:</b>
            <ul style="color:olive;">
              <li>Allow you to have automatic version of attachments for same file name and extension.</li>
              <li>Allow you to control for what models/objects you do not want versioning of attachments / documents.</li>
              <li>Full history of Document versions for next and previous versions information.</li>
              <li>System will auto detect if same file name and extension is present then system will create versioning of attachment.</li>
              <li>For more details please see below screenshots and watch Video.</li>
            </ul>
        </p>
          <p style="color:CRIMSON;"><b>Menus Available:</b>
            <ul  style="color:olive;">
              <li>Settings</li>
              <ul>
                <li>Technical</li>
                <ul>
                    <li>Document Versioning</li>
                <ul><li>Attachments Version Config</li></ul></ul>
              </ul>
            </ul>
          </p>
        <b>
   </div>
